  "texts": [
    "FPN integrates bottom-up and top-down pathways to produce multi-scale feature maps while maintaining semantic information.",
    "This architecture enhances detection capabilities for small objects across various resolutions and sizes.",
    "The semantic gap in feature maps derived from different levels in Mask R-CNN can significantly degrade detection accuracy, particularly in cluttered scenes.",
